      "description": "CFD simulation converged nominally. RH = 0.88. One early restart was required after the solver was relaunched following a job-scheduler timeout; the partial restart result was discarded and a fresh run accepted. No investigation of whether the timeout exposed a reproducibility edge case was conducted."
