    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required Gradation 2 level for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Predicted RH values at all five operating points fall below the RH < 1 acceptance criterion with adequate margin. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim that the CFD model identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Software quality assurance was confirmed via regression testing and version control; all validation runs completed nominally without solver failures or reported numerical exceptions.",
